>\n<br />\n她表示，非常關心慈雲山區內多個公共屋邨近日出現多宗確診個案，已經指示民政事務總署統籌為慈正邨及毗鄰有確診個案的屋邨住戶安排免費病毒檢測。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又批評，一些別有用心的人藉此散播謠言，說甚麼有內地醫療團隊到香港的公營醫院提供診治服務，或把港人的基因樣本送回內地等，不斷藉機抹黑中央及破壞特區和中央的關係，實在令人氣憤。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539810-20200725.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539810-20200725.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=8cac31a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539810-20200725.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8d53954e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539810-20200725.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:16:11.000Z","msg":"屌 之前先話唔係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人計過佢反過幾多次口"},{"pid":"8e1e6403bfafb5efbba8ddbf26341b6c870a942d","tid":2123873,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"其實放緊風"},{"pid":"c2a49faabe8eb818b18cfd2b188bc9fcacd38866","tid":2123873,"uid":97701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:27:19.000Z","msg":"縮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ff0b67cb5ff7ed0f6973bcc99687046e48e9e0","tid":2123873,"uid":123920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:29:30.000Z","msg":"回力標<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}